OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fwindy for a time overnight, with
OL,7,Foccasional blustery showers, spreading
OL,8,Feast to most parts by midnight. Winds
OL,9,Feasing a little through the early
OL,10,Fhours of Easter Sunday, but staying
OL,11,Frather breezy and cloudy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FSome early sunshine, initially
OL,14,Facross western parts before spreading
OL,15,Feast. Cloud then building with
OL,16,Foccasional blustery showers
OL,17,Fdeveloping, before largely clearing
OL,18,Feast through the afternoon. A little
OL,19,Fcooler than Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
